title: Watch: Mothers try to figure out if objects are dog toys or sex toys (NSFW)
text:
You're going to want to wash your eyes out after this.
Distractify sat down a selection of mothers, blindfolded them and asked them to identify whether or not toys they were given were of the canine variety or the sexual variety.
Awkward would be an understatement. We can't even imagine what it's like for these women's kids.
Via Distractify
